1, \"to\": 848, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nasar seemed barely troubled.\", \"from\": 850, \"to\": 879, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.571320603590697e-18, \"text\": \"Nasar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Pausing an extra beat with the bar on his chest, he grinned, before hoisting a world record 224kg over his head for a total of 404kg, another record.\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 1029, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nasar has reportedly lifted even greater weights in training.\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1092, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1031, \"end\": 1036, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.571320603590697e-18, \"text\": \"Nasar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have visualised the win many times and I succeeded each time,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked if he was playing to the camera, Nasar grinned.\", \"from\": 1170, \"to\": 1228, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1214, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.571320603590697e-18, \"text\": \"Nasar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nasar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes the emotions that I show, I cannot control,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1230, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Sometimes I do not even remember what happened on the stage.\\\"\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Colombian Yeison Lopez was second on 390kg.\", \"from\": 1359, \"to\": 1402, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1376, \"end\": 1381, \"title\": \"htt